Escherworld
David Borland
Paul Brannan
David Stone

Starting the program

Use ewsound for sound, and ew for no sound.  To enable helmet display, use
the --helmet option.  Note that bird control is not yet implemented.

Navigation

Use the mouse or keyboard to navigate.  The left mouse button controls
zoom, while the middle mouse button controls rotation about angle theta and
phi.  The right mouse button will bring up a menu.

Keyboard controls

T       Toggle textures
L       Toggle lighting
X       Toggle axes
W       Toggle weapon
F	Toggle linear filtering
E	Toggle terrain
G	Toggle gridlines
C	Toggle craters
S	Toggle smooth shading
\,K	Toggle motion lock
+       Zoom in
-       Zoom out
Q	Quit

